00:22:44.855 --> 00:22:49.450
profile--there should be a
hyphen there--(P_1*,

00:22:49.450 --> 00:22:56.021
P_2*,
…all the way up to

00:22:56.021 --> 00:23:02.592
P_N*),
is a mixed strategy Nash

00:23:02.592 --> 00:23:12.284
Equilibrium if for each Player
i--so for each Player i--that

00:23:12.284 --> 00:23:20.005
player's mixed strategy
P_i* is a best

00:23:20.005 --> 00:23:29.040
response for Player i to the
strategies everyone else is

00:23:29.040 --> 00:23:37.814
picking P _-i*.
So I'm exploiting,

00:23:37.814 --> 00:23:47.390
by now, a well developed
notation for player strategies.

00:23:47.390 --> 00:23:50.547
So this definition of Nash
Equilibrium, it's exactly the

00:23:50.547 --> 00:23:54.106
same as the definition of Nash
Equilibrium we've been using now

00:23:54.106 --> 00:23:57.466
